::Spears::
She kissed him and didn't want to stop.  She felt his hand move over 
her body.  She sighed as he did.  She was totaly fixed on his kiss. 
She didn't want her lips to part from his.  She forgot about the 
soot, the burnt ship, the other bots, everything.  The only thing she 
knew, or thought of, was him.
She could feel his spark was racing as fast as her's.  She raised her 
arms and gently glided her hand up and down his back.  She had her 
other arm hold her close to him.  She kissed him and felt her spark 
go for him.  Her spark, mind and body told her, she was his, no 
matter what.
